  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras/48c92a6c00c608128775148e43380513.poster.avif?t=1739966420\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras/48c92a6c00c608128775148e43380513.webm?t=1739966420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras/48c92a6c00c608128775148e43380513.mp4?t=1739966420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>Prove Your Skills or Get Some Practice</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re looking to showcase your driving and parking expertise or you’re in need of some practice, <i>Reverse Problem</i> has you covered. Master every aspect of truck maneuvering, from tight spaces to tricky angles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras/920f786e387506e5f0e1cb5c59bc9535.avif?t=1739966420\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras_big/920f786e387506e5f0e1cb5c59bc9535.avif?t=1739966420 width=800 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore 4 Unique Locations</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel across four distinct locations, each offering its own set of challenges and driving styles. Adapt to new environments and refine your skills with each journey.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras/2fce17444485b73ff1b2774322aa3d51.avif?t=1739966420\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras_big/2fce17444485b73ff1b2774322aa3d51.avif?t=1739966420 width=800 height=186 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete 200 Handcrafted Levels Designed by Pros</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on 200 expertly designed levels created by real truck drivers. With 100 unique vehicles, you’ll face a variety of scenarios that test your abilities and push your limits in every situation. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras/eb8b0842026c4ec6d2c752d307a4d4cf.poster.avif?t=1739966420\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras/eb8b0842026c4ec6d2c752d307a4d4cf.webm?t=1739966420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3355020/extras/eb8b0842026c4ec6d2c752d307a4d4cf.mp4?t=1739966420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>More challenges in the minigame modes!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sandbox </strong>– Always wondered if you could reverse a truck into that tricky local terminal dock? In <i>Sandbox Mode</i>, create your own custom scenarios and put your skills to the test.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blind Spot </strong>– Test how many times you can park your truck in a row while avoiding collisions, as the time steadily decreases with each attempt.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slipstream </strong>– Test your ability to stay aware of your surroundings and maintain control under pressure as you navigate your truck through a maze of moving blocks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Supported Control Types</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keyboard and mouse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xbox Gamepad controller (other types of gamepads not tested)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Notice!</strong> - No steering wheel support currently available.</p>",
